        {
            "title": "新盤銷情｜大角咀映居晒冷盡賣122伙 內地客5200萬掃8伙作投資收租",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"525\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PYW_1_cGLdfQaBpixui.Ew--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc3NA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/5c129e905b36124f0a559f35f33ace80\" width=\"651\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">建灝地產及市建局合作發展大角咀新盤映居今日（3月27日）首輪銷售，晒冷盡推全盤122伙，截至傍晚，據悉大手客時段沽約69伙。發展商表示，錄得最少2組大手買家各斥資逾5,000萬元連購8伙，其中一組內地客以5,200萬元購入8伙作投資收租之用。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">樓盤開售前累收近3,550票，超額認購逾28倍，今日首輪銷售分3組進行，包括A1、A2及B組買家，A1組買家可選購最少3伙及不多於12伙，A2組買家必須選購2伙，而於A1組及A2組買家合共揀購的單位總數最多為80伙。餘下42伙單位留予B組買家，可選購1伙或2伙。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0f3982e8-d9c7-3953-9641-f87d0e98c06c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大手客A1及A2組時段，錄得約69宗成交。中原地產亞太區副主席兼住宅部總裁陳永傑表示，該行買家出席率高達8成，以九龍客為主，佔7成。客源當中，用家及長線投資者各佔一半，用家以小型家庭、來港專才及年輕上車客為主，長線投資者當中不乏大手客，亦有數組買家有意揀選4伙。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美聯物業高級董事布少明指，有內地客斥資約5,200萬元購入8個單位作投資收租之用。客源方面以九龍區為主，佔約7成，預期該項目用家佔6成，投資者佔4成，項目呎租可達 75元，租金回報率逾4厘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">樓盤位於大角咀埃華街3號，屬單幢物業，提供122伙，戶型主要為一房連書房間隔，實用面積301至347方呎，折實579萬至888.8萬元，折實呎價16,880至25,614元。預計關鍵日期為今年10月底。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/>免費物業投資講座！<br/>報名 <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"https\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:https://rb.gy/nl0vm;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://rb.gy/nl0vm\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://rb.gy/nl0vm</a></p></div>",
